webpackJsonp([0x80f5aaaabc52],{453:function(a,n){a.exports={data:{site:{siteMetadata:{title:"Life is a YOLO game",author:"Henry Wu"}},markdownRemark:{id:"/home/circleci/project/src/pages/react-native-touchables.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark",html:'<h2>樣式上的差異</h2>\n<p>在 React Native，如果需要觸控區域，我們有兩個選擇：<code class="language-text">&lt;TouchableWithoutFeedback /&gt;</code> 與 <code class="language-text">&lt;TouchableHighlight /&gt;</code>。根據文件，官方並不希望我們使用前者，原因基於前者不會對觸控產生回饋，會讓使用者對觸控是否有效產生不必要的誤解。</p>\n<p>實際使用之後，我發現兩者另外一項區別在於 <code class="language-text">&lt;TouchableWithoutFeedback /&gt;</code> 沒有預設樣式，實際使用起來就像是一個隱形的容器，包住內部的元素，但又不會與內部的容器互相影響；而 <code class="language-text">&lt;TouchableHighlight /&gt;</code> 本身則會形成一個區塊，會與內部的元素相互影響。至於之前的版本曾經有使用者提出 <code class="language-text">&lt;TouchableHighlight /&gt;</code> 可能是為了產生回饋的視覺效果，而有效能上的問題。但在 <code class="language-text">0.28.x</code> 之後，至少我實際使用到現在還沒有遇到嚴重的效能問題，即使是在最複雜的編輯履歷頁面也沒有。</p>\n<h2><code class="language-text">&lt;View /&gt;</code> 與自訂 component 的規格差異</h2>\n<p>官方文件建議如果要在 <code class="language-text">Touchable</code> 系列裡使用多個 component，如以下的形式，直接寫是行不通的。</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight" data-language="jsx">\n      <pre class="language-jsx"><code class="language-jsx"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>TouchableHighlight</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ChildOne</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span>\n  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ChildTwo</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span>\n<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>TouchableHighlight</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>必須改寫成以下形式。</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight" data-language="jsx">\n      <pre class="language-jsx"><code class="language-jsx"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>TouchableHighlight</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>View</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ChildOne</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span>\n    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ChildTwo</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span>\n  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>View</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>TouchableHighlight</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>而重點就在這個 <code class="language-text">&lt;View /&gt;</code>。這個 <code class="language-text">&lt;View /&gt;</code> 在 <code class="language-text">0.28.x</code> 時不能以自訂的 component 取代。例如以下的程式碼，在 <code class="language-text">0.28.x</code> 有一定的機率造成 <code class="language-text">Touchable</code> 失去效果。</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight" data-language="jsx">\n      <pre class="language-jsx"><code class="language-jsx"><span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token function-variable function">MyComp</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">{</span>children<span class="token punctuation">}</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">=></span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>\n  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>View</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n    <span class="token punctuation">{</span>children<span class="token punctuation">}</span>\n  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>View</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span>\n\n<span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token function-variable function">Touchable</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">=></span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>\n  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>TouchableHighlight</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>MyComp</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ChildOne</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span>\n      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ChildTwo</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span>\n    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>MyComp</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>TouchableHighlight</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>如果寫成以上的形式，則 React Native 在執行的時候會展開成以下形式。</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight" data-language="jsx">\n      <pre class="language-jsx"><code class="language-jsx"><span class="token keyword">const</span> <span class="token function-variable function">Touchable</span> <span class="token operator">=</span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span> <span class="token operator">=></span> <span class="token punctuation">(</span>\n  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>TouchableHighlight</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>MyComp</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>View</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ChildOne</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span>\n        <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>ChildTwo</span> <span class="token punctuation">/></span></span>\n      <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>View</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n    <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>MyComp</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n  <span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>TouchableHighlight</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>\n<span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">;</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>這時候會發生錯誤導致 React Native 無法執行。原因是 <code class="language-text">&lt;MyComp /&gt;</code> 並不是一個 native component，因此當 <code class="language-text">Touchable</code> 在為這個 component 注入一些屬性時，會發生某些 <code class="language-text">&lt;View /&gt;</code> 有定義 function 在自訂 component 中沒有被定義 (<code class="language-text">[函數名稱] is undefined</code>) 的錯誤。</p>\n<p>根據 <a href="https://facebook.github.io/react-native/docs/direct-manipulation.html">Direct Manipulation</a> 中的說明，如果要將一個自訂的 component <strong>偽裝</strong> 成 native component，則需要實作 <code class="language-text">setNativeProps</code> 這個 function，然後把 native props 傳遞給要自訂的 component。</p>\n<p>但實際測試之後，<code class="language-text">setNativeProps</code> 的效果並不如預期地是 100% 正常運作。因此建議如果沒有特別的需求，盡量還是直接使用 <code class="language-text">&lt;View /&gt;</code> 來包裝 child component。</p>\n<p>我知道畫面上一堆 <code class="language-text">&lt;View /&gt;</code> 會讓可讀性變得非常差，否則我們也不需要自己實作自己的 component，但這是目前已知唯一 100% 有效的實作方法。</p>',frontmatter:{title:"React Native 的觸控區域",date:"July 29, 2016"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/react-native-touchables/",previous:{fields:{slug:"/react-native-moment-locale/"},frontmatter:{title:"在 React Native 中使用 moment.js 無法載入語系檔案"}},next:{fields:{slug:"/react-native-upgrade-and-flexbox/"},frontmatter:{title:"React Native 從 0.28.x 升級與 flexbox"}}}}}});
